10 CHAPTER 38. DAMAGE RECOVERY FUND
11 §2251. Recovery fund; creation
12 The department shall establish a fund for the collection of funds recovered
13 by the state for damage to state property which occurs from traffic accidents or other
14 accidents that cause damage to state property on state highways.
15 §2252. Use of funds
16 A. Funds collected under this Chapter shall be utilized by the department to
17 repair the damage in the district in which it was caused or to refund the payment for
18 repairs from damage caused by traffic accidents already paid by the district or by the
19 local governing authority.
